Installing Ailurus
==================

  Requirements
  ------------

    * python
    * python-gtk2
    * python-notify
    * python-vte
    * python-apt
    * python-gobject
    * python-dbus
    * procps
    * unzip
    * policykit-gnome | policykit-kde | policykit-1-gnome

  Installation
  ------------

    To install Ailurus, perform the following command as root:
    
      $ python setup.py install
      
  Run Ailurus
  -----------

	You can launch the program by typing "ailurus" at the command line.